{"tid":569184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民熱話：倫敦地鐵自拍　的哥錯怪容祖兒撐Uber","createTime":"2018-02-22T12:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T13:07:49.000Z","uid":121245,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c593f06e8ec15e2d7b2e346271d566fa1c6159c6","tid":569184,"uid":121245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:45:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180222/mobile/bkn-20180222161045837-0222_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180222%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180222161045837-0222_00822_001.html&d=jy%2FSht6CnzJSEoys9N7VJwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=539e1740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180222/mobile/bkn-20180222161045837-0222_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港澳新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民熱話：倫敦地鐵自拍　的哥錯怪容祖兒撐Uber<br />\n02月22日(四) 16:10   <br />\n的哥發文炮轟歌星容祖兒幫Uber賣廣告。（Facebook「的士司機資訊網」圖片）<br />\n的哥發文炮轟歌星容祖兒幫Uber賣廣告。（Facebook「的士司機資訊網」圖片）<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n香港的士司機痛恨Uber爭生意，因此不時會找機會攻擊對手。今日（22日）藝人容祖兒更「躺着也中槍」，無辜牽涉入這場鬥爭中。容祖兒於Facebook貼出倫敦地鐵自拍照，並指地鐵只需15分鐘，比的士45分鐘快。卻惹來一名的士司機誤解祖兒英文「underground」為「Uber」，因此在Facebook批評容祖兒為Uber賣廣告，淪為網民笑柄。 <br />\n<br />\n歌星容祖兒（Joey）在英國倫敦外遊，她在其個人Facebook帳戶上載一張在當地地鐵的自拍照，並說：「taxi45分鐘underground（地鐵）15分鐘，仲駛（使）揀嘅」本想說在倫敦搭地鐵比的士更快，不料被本港一名的士司機「借刀」，用來「抽水」攻擊對手Uber。可惜他的回應反映他對該貼文的理解有連番謬誤。 <br />\n<br />\n首先，他誤當「underground」為「Uber」，轉載到「的士司機資訊網 Taxi」痛斥：「唔好玩啦五分鐘都唔等啦，幫烏龜爸買（賣）廣告？」除了理解錯「underground」一字，有網民亦發現該的哥對時間觀念亦有所誤差，恥笑他：「45分鐘同15分鐘相差5分鐘？咁佢唔止英文唔掂，連數學都要惡補下。」亦有人指出「睇埋打卡」，地點在倫敦而非香港，遠不在的士司機搵食地盤之中，不明白他點解會因此批評Joey。 <br />\n<br />\n雖然該帖文已被刪除，但該發文者已「回不了頭」，被網民截圖並在社交平台瘋傳，一眾網民湧出恥笑該「衝出嚟」批評的的士司機，嘲笑「有個U字就當Uber，的士佬係時候讀多啲書增值下自己，唔好成日衝出嚟X。」 <br />\n<br />\n好心的士狗讀多啲書先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c8942406da17b60644b30a833a4565bb72b14c","tid":569184,"uid":22054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:46:12.000Z","msg":"又係因報，的佢老母哥咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d194dd10f40435df7689a734525e3f96187d4098","tid":569184,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:47:37.000Z","msg":"識字就唔洗揸的屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1a08a95d1d0f6ac24fd6615c9824754608be0a","tid":569184,"uid":121245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d194dd10f40435df7689a734525e3f96187d4098","tid":569184,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:47:37.000Z","msg":"識字就唔洗揸的屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:54:55.000Z","msg":"有時冇料扮四條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2d3f2b8fe79063140735da0ad3097bb98d56c4","tid":569184,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:03:43.000Z","msg":"的佢老母哥咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb80cf1b58331e7dbe091bd8297df9dc6e027170","tid":569184,"uid":98289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:07:49.000Z","msg":"的哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n白粉報d 記者食係咪take 左嘢先寫稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.g